<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Chatka Matka Restaurant</title>

<style>

body{
margin:0;
font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
background:#000;
color:#fff;
}

header{
background:#f5c400;
color:#000;
padding:20px;
text-align:center;
font-size:32px;
font-weight:bold;
letter-spacing:2px;
}

.hero{
background:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604908176997-43188c6f3a2c') center/cover;
height:350px;
display:flex;
align-items:center;
justify-content:center;
flex-direction:column;
text-align:center;
}

.hero h1{
font-size:45px;
background:rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
padding:10px 20px;
}

.btn{
background:#f5c400;
color:#000;
padding:12px 25px;
border:none;
font-size:18px;
cursor:pointer;
margin-top:15px;
font-weight:bold;
}

.section{
padding:40px;
text-align:center;
}

.menu{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
gap:20px;
margin-top:30px;
}

.card{
background:#111;
padding:20px;
border:1px solid #f5c400;
}

.card h3{
color:#f5c400;
}

.price{
float:right;
}

.special{
background:#f5c400;
color:#000;
padding:30px;
margin:40px 0;
}

.reviews{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
gap:20px;
}

.review{
background:#111;
padding:20px;
border:1px solid #f5c400;
}

.rating{
color:gold;
font-size:20px;
}

footer{
background:#f5c400;
color:#000;
text-align:center;
padding:20px;
margin-top:40px;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
CHATKA MATKA
</header>

<section class="hero">
<h1>Taste Ka Tadka</h1>
<button class="btn">Book a Table</button>
</section>

<section class="section">
<h2>Our Menu</h2>

<div class="menu">

<div class="card">
<h3>Indian Breads</h3>
<p>Plain Tandoori Roti <span class="price">₹13</span></p>
<p>Butter Tandoori Roti <span class="price">₹15</span></p>
<p>Tawa Plain Roti <span class="price">₹9</span></p>
<p>Tawa Butter Roti <span class="price">₹12</span></p>
<p>Plain Naan <span class="price">₹40</span></p>
<p>Butter Naan <span class="price">₹60</span></p>
<p>Lachha Parantha <span class="price">₹60</span></p>
<p>Missi Roti <span class="price">₹50</span></p>
<p>Stuffed Naan <span class="price">₹80</span></p>
<p>Onion Kulcha <span class="price">₹70</span></p>
<p>Garlic Naan <span class="price">₹80</span></p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Raita</h3>
<p>Fruit Raita <span class="price">₹90</span></p>
<p>Veg Raita <span class="price">₹80</span></p>
<p>Aloo Raita <span class="price">₹80</span></p>
<p>Boondi Raita <span class="price">₹80</span></p>
<p>Plain Raita <span class="price">₹70</span></p>
<p>Dahi <span class="price">₹70</span></p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Indian Rice</h3>
<p>Steamed Rice <span class="price">₹80</span></p>
<p>Jeera Rice <span class="price">₹100</span></p>
<p>Veg Pulao <span class="price">₹120</span></p>
<p>Chatka Matka Pulao <span class="price">₹160</span></p>
<p>Veg Biryani <span class="price">₹160</span></p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Salad</h3>
<p>Green Salad <span class="price">₹60</span></p>
<p>Cucumber Salad <span class="price">₹60</span></p>
<p>Kachumber Salad <span class="price">₹60</span></p>
</div>

</div>
</section>

<section class="special">
<h2>Chef Special</h2>
<h1>PANEER TIKKA</h1>
<p>Fresh grilled paneer with Indian spices that makes every bite unforgettable.</p>
</section>

<section class="section">
<h2>Customer Reviews</h2>

<div class="reviews">

<div class="review">
<h3>Rahul</h3>
<div class="rating">★★★★★</div>
<p>Best Paneer Tikka I ever had. Amazing taste.</p>
</div>

<div class="review">
<h3>Neha</h3>
<div class="rating">★★★★★</div>
<p>Affordable food and great Indian breads.</p>
</div>

<div class="review">
<h3>Arjun</h3>
<div class="rating">★★★★★</div>
<p>Perfect place for family dinner.</p>
</div>

</div>
</section>

<section class="section">
<h2>Reserve Your Table</h2>
<button class="btn">Book Table Now</button>
</section>

<footer>
<h3>Thank You For Visiting Chatka Matka</h3>
<p>We are dedicated to serving delicious food with love.</p>
</footer>

</body>
  </html>
